b\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Θεοῖς\">Θ\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-text=\"Καταχθονίοις\">[..]\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al2-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">2\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Σωτηρ\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Σωτηρ\">ΣΩΤ[..\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003Cbr id=\"al3-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">3\u003C/span>[\u003Cspan dir=\"ltr\" class=\"gap\">---\u003C/span>]\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001328_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001328_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001328.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001328-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>\u003Cspan>Text based on photographs\u003C/span>\u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 2\">line.2: \u003Cspan>Kaibel, Korhonen: Σωτ[ῆρ? ---]\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>To the subterranean deities, Sot---\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Agli dèi inferi, Sot---\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>The invocation to the subterranean deities is followed by the name of the deceased, probably \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Σωτῆρ\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Σώταιρος\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Σώτειρα\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Σωτηρία\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Σωτηρίδας\u003C/span>, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Σωτηρίς\u003C/span> (attested in an inscription from Catania dated to the 3rd-5th cent. CE: IG 14.550 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001369\" target=\"_blank\">ISic001369\u003C/a>), \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Σωτήριχος\u003C/span> (attested in an inscription from Catania dated to the imperial age: CIL 10.7054 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000338\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000338\u003C/a>): on the names, see LGPN 3A: 417-419.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">507\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 130 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\">\u003Cp>Θ in a simple form, with a straight and attached cross-bar, squared lunate Σ and squared cursive Ω.\u003C/p> Lines 1-2  19-22  Interlineation line 1 to 2  not recorded  \u003C/div>\u003Cd