rag\u003C/principal>\n                \u003Cfunder>John Fell OUP Research Fund\u003C/funder>\n\t   \u003Cfunder>\u003Cref target=\"https://cordis.europa.eu/project/id/885040\">ERC Advanced Grant no.885040\u003C/ref>\u003C/funder>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JP\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0003-3819-8537\">Jonathan Prag\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>original data collection and editing\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"martaf\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>editing, translation and commentary\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"JCu\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0002-6686-3728\">James Cummings\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>conversion to EpiDoc\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n                \u003CrespStmt>\n                    \u003Cname xml:id=\"AA\" ref=\"http://orcid.org/0000-0001-7077-0703\">Alex Antoniou\u003C/name>\n                    \u003Cresp>EpiDoc editing and English translation\u003C/resp>\n                \u003C/respStmt>\n\t    \u003CrespStmt>\n     \t       \u003Cname xml:id=\"SS\" ref=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0003-3914-9569\">Simona Stoyanova\u003C/name>\n     \t       \u003Cresp>standardisation of template and tidying up encoding\u003C/resp>\n \t   \u003C/respStmt>\n               \u003C/titleStmt>\n            \u003CpublicationStmt>\n                \u003Cauthority>I.Sicily\u003C/authority>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"filename\">ISic001328\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"TM\">492934\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDR\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDH\"/>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"EDCS\">39101699\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\">140822\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"PHI\">316238\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"URI\">http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001328\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cidno type=\"DOI\" when=\"2020-12-18\">10.5281/zenodo.4353467\u003C/idno>\n                \u003Cavailability>\n                    \u003Clicence target=\"http://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/\">Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence.\u003C/licence>\n                \u003C/availability>\n            \u003C/publicationStmt>\n            \u003CsourceDesc>\n                \u003CmsDesc>\n                    \u003CmsIdentifier>\n                        \u003Ccountry>Italy\u003C/country>\n                        \u003Cregion>Sicily\u003C/region>\n                        \u003Csettlement>Catania\u003C/settlement>\n                        \u003Crepository role=\"museum\" ref=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/museum/018\">Museo Civico di Catania\u003C/repository>\n                        \u003C!--No inventory number found-->\n                        \u003C!--Adding location for old id numbers if available-->\n                        \u003CaltIdentifier>\n                            \u003Csettlement/>\n                            \u003Crepository/>\n                            \u003Cidno type=\"old\"/>\n                        \u003C/altIdentifier>\n                    \u003C/msIdentifier>\n                    \u003CmsContents>\n                        \u003CtextLang mainLang=\"grc\">Ancient Greek\u003C/textLang>\n                    \u003C/msContents>\n                    \u003CphysDesc>\n                        \u003CobjectDesc>\n                            \u003CsupportDesc>\n                                \u003Csupport>\u003Cp>Fragment of an opisthographic marble plaque; the upper left corner is preserved, broken to right and below. On the reverse is a more recent Latin epitaph (IMusCatania 156 = \u003Cref sameAs=\"ISic003270.xml\">ISic003270\u003C/ref>).\u003C/p>\n                                    \u003Cmaterial ana=\"#material.stone.marble\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/material/lod/48.html\">marble\u003C/material>\n                                    \u003CobjectType ana=\"#object.plaque\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/objtyp/lod/259.html\">plaque\u003C/objectType>\n                                    \u003Cdimensions>\u003C!--measurements from Korhonen-->\n                                        \u003Cheight unit=\"cm\">10\u003C/height>\n                                        \u003Cwidth unit=\"cm\">12\u003C/width>\n                                        \u003Cdepth unit=\"cm\">2.3\u003C/depth>\n                                    \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003C/support>\n                                \u003Ccondition ana=\"#condition.fragment\"/>\n\t\t    \u003C/supportDesc>\n                            \u003ClayoutDesc>\n                                \u003Clayout>\n                                    \u003Crs ana=\"#execution.chiselled\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/writing/lod/1\">chiselled\u003C/rs>\n                                \t\u003Cdamage/>\n\t\t\t\u003C/layout>\n                            \u003C/layoutDesc>\n                        \u003C/objectDesc>\n                        \u003ChandDesc>\n                            \u003ChandNote>\u003Cp>Θ in a simple form, with a straight and attached cross-bar, squared lunate Σ and squared cursive Ω.\u003C/p>\u003C!--measurements from Korhonen-->\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Lines 1-2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"letterHeight\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\" atLeast=\"19\" atMost=\"22\">19-22\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                                \u003Clocus from=\"line1\" to=\"line2\">Interlineation line 1 to 2\u003C/locus>\n                                \u003Cdimensions type=\"interlinear\">\n                                    \u003Cheight unit=\"mm\">not recorded\u003C/height>\n                                \u003C/dimensions>\n                            \u003C/handNote>\n                        \u003C/handDesc>\n                    \u003C/physDesc>\n                    \u003Chistory>\n                        \u003Corigin>\n                            \u003CorigPlace>\u003Cregion>Sicilia\u003C/region>\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"ancient\" ref=\"http://pleiades.stoa.org/places/462270\">Catina\u003C/placeName>\t\t\n                                \u003CplaceName type=\"modern\" ref=\"http://sws.geonames.org/2525068\">Catania\u003C/placeName> \n                            \t\u003Cgeo>37.49223, 15.07041\u003C/geo>\n\t\t\u003C/origPlace>\n                            \u003CorigDate datingMethod=\"#julian\" notBefore-custom=\"0201\" notAfter-custom=\"0300\">3rd century CE\u003C/origDate>\n                        \u003C/origin>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"found\">Original discovery not recorded, but assumed to be from Catania (“visto che si tratta di un frammento poco notevole, con un’iscrizione greca su una faccia, e una latina sull’altra, sembra preferibile la provenienza locale” Korhonen 2004: 242).\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\">Observed by Kaibel in Museo Biscari, later by Korhonen in magazzino superiore, Collezione Biscari.\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cprovenance type=\"observed\" subtype=\"autopsied\">None\u003C/provenance>\n                        \u003Cacquisition/>\n                    \u003C/history>\n                \u003C/msDesc>\n            \u003C/sourceDesc>\n        \u003C/fileDesc>\n        \u003CencodingDesc>\n             \u003Cp>Encoded following the latest EpiDoc guidelines\u003C/p>\n             \u003Cxi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n             